    <div class="timeline">

        <div class="timeline-entry">
            <h3>1941</h3>
            <p>Norwegian exiles and refugees were hosted in Dumfries during WWII.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-entry">
            <h3>1943</h3>
            <p>The Scottish Norwegian Society (Glasgow) was founded.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-entry">
            <h3>2016</h3>
            <p>75th Anniversary celebrated with a commemorative service in Dumfries.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-entry">
            <h3>Today</h3>
            <p>The Society continues to promote Norwegian culture and heritage in Scotland.</p>
